{{Infobox Underground Item |name = Shards |image = [[File:Red_Shard.png|90px]] |caption = In-Game image of the ''Red Shard''. |price = 1 {{Diamonds}} |location = [[Underground]] [[Berry Master]] }}
==Description== '''Shards''' are big items you can mine from the [[Underground]], obtain from Daily Deals, or trade for with the Hoenn [[Berry Master]]. They can then be used, together with [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at [[Shard Traders]].
